name: ComparatorUtils_maxTest
description: Unit tests for the max functionality of ComparatorUtils with different comparators.

test_cases.name: testMaxWithDefaultComparator
test_cases.description: Tests the max functionality of ComparatorUtils with a null comparator, which should use the default comparator.

test_cases.name: testMaxWithCustomComparator
test_cases.description: Tests the max functionality of ComparatorUtils with a custom natural order comparator.

test_cases.name: testMaxWithCustomComparatorReversed
test_cases.description: Tests the max functionality of ComparatorUtils with a custom reversed order comparator.
